cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with domain adaptation and deep learning, which are topics commonly found in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on image classification and semantic segmentation, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The use of deep self-training also suggests cs.LG as a likely sub-category.
